-16 px-4 bg-[#f5f5e9]"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full justify-center"><h3 class="text-xl font-decima-mono text-[#6f7c64] mb-4 font-bold">FIND US</h3><div class="space-y-2 font-decima-mono text-stone-600"><p>1/351 Mt Dandenong Tourist Rd</p><p>Sassafras Victoria 3787</p><a href="tel:97553017" data-testid="link-phone" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1 text-[#5a6652] font-bold hover:text-[#6f7c64] underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 mt-2"><span>9755 3017</span></a><div class="mt-2"><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/m5M4seq1sEAtp5ZV8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-testid="link-google-maps" class="inline-block text-[#5a6652] font-bold hover:text-[#6f7c64] underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2">Open In Google Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full justify-center"><h3 class="text-xl font-decima-mono text-[#6f7c64] mb-4 font-bold">OPENING HOURS</h3><div class="space-y-2 font-decima-mono text-stone-600"><p>Monday &amp; Tuesday — Closed</p><p>Wednesday &amp; Thursday - 5pm - 10pm</p><p>Friday &amp; Saturday - 12pm - 3pm &amp; 5pm - Late</p><p>Sunday - 12pm - 3pm</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 px-4 bg-[#6f7c64]"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#f5f5e9] mb-16 font-decima-mono text-center">WHAT'S ON</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8"><div data-testid="gallery-item-0" class="flex flex-col space-y-4"><div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden aspect-square"><img src="https://houseoffras.com.au/assets/locals-night-hk2Z04Vh.jpg" alt="Wood-fired pizza with fresh herbs and wine" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy"></div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="flex items-baseline justify-between"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#f5f5e9] font-decima-mono">LOCAL'S NIGHT</h3><